Package gov.cdc.izgw.v2tofhir.segment

Class OBXParser

java.lang.Object
gov.cdc.izgw.v2tofhir.segment.AbstractStructureParser
gov.cdc.izgw.v2tofhir.segment.AbstractSegmentParser
gov.cdc.izgw.v2tofhir.segment.OBXParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
Processor<ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.Message,ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.Segment>
@Produces(segment="OBX", resource=org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Observation.class, extra={org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Immunization.class,org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.ImmunizationRecommendation.class}) public class OBXParser extends AbstractSegmentParser
OBXParser parses any OBX segments in a message to an Immunization if the message is a VXU or an response to an immunization query. It merges OBX information into the Immunization or ImmunizationRecommendation resource where appropriate, otherwise it creates new Observation resources.
Author:
Audacious Inquiry
